COntainers are Isolated Environments, If we can each Container to talk to ech other we need to Create a Network for them...... ( e.g Frontend & Backend )
For that Use these Commands..!!

Step 1 - Create the network

*  docker network create auth-network

Step 2 - Connect both containers to it :

docker network connect auth-network frontendcontainer

docker network connect auth-network backendcontainer

Step 3 - Verify both are connected :

docker network inspect auth-network



